docs.lead_paragraph: HOLLYWOOD. TO the average tourist, looking around Los Angeles for tangible manifestations of fabulous "Holly wood," it might seem ironic that there should be any question about the health, prosperity and permanence of the great film-producing industry.

headline.main: Communique From Hollywood And Vine; Are movies 'an empire falling apart'? A critic analyzes Hollywood's dilemma.
